        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/miami/scene_flamingo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5a9a03d7-0e61-4f36-b8a0-b98f74f3c20d).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47.\r\rYour targets today are Hector Delgado and Abdul Suleiman. Hector serves as the touchpoint for the Delgado Cartel&apos;s seedy dealings in foreign countries. He is meeting today with Abdul, who plans to fork over precious Saudi Arabian intel in exchange for cartel prescene in a key international meeting for maritime trade. \r\rThe two are in Miami today to watch the Global Innovation Race, and our client, the Saudi Arabian government, wants both men dead as a permanent message.",
